description:
This is a 8 minute workout called 'BEGINNER CALISTHENICS WORKOUT' from the channel Meli.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let me know if you try this Push Pull Calisthenics workout, I’ve made it specifically for beginners, so DON’T STRESS. 

There are progression exercises for each calisthenics exercise, so you can work your way up in intensity depending on your level

I’m committed to helping you feel your best and MOST capable self in your body, and this workout was made to train the FOUNDATIONAL STRENGTH you need, which will benefit your lifting too 

If this video helped you, this one will help you more ↓

The Training Your Body Desperately Needs
